description.plain: With a voice reminiscent of the late Pop Smoke, DUSTY LOCANE is fixing to blow up. LOCANE, from Canarsie Brooklyn, has already amassed over thirty million streams on his first single, “R60LLXN N CONTROLLXN FREESTYLE.”

description.plain: Reminiscent of late New York rapper Pop Smoke, Dusty Locane comes in with a drill hit, “R60LLXN N CONTROLLXN (FREESTYLE)”. The song skyrocketed him into the hip-hop spotlight with most of the attention on how similar he sounded to the late Pop Smoke. Over a hard drill beat, Dusty reps his neighborhood, shouts out his set, and makes sure people know he is ready to ride always.

songs.full_title: ROLANDO (Caught in the Rain) by DUSTY LOCANE
songs.title: ROLANDO (Caught in the Rain)

description.plain:
“Rolando (Caught in the Rain)” is DUSTY LOCANE’s second breakout hit, after the release of “ROLLIN N CONTROLLIN FREESTYLE.”

The song, produced by BassoBeatz, has Dusty rapping about his life, gang activity, and telling the listener what he reps.

The beat has a sample from the artist Fousheé with the producer saying he got the sample from the platform Splice, and was originally posted as a type beat on Youtube under the name “Caught In The Rain.”
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0Y5HcmLHyw&ab_channel=BassoBeatz

songs.title: RUMBLE

description.plain:
DUSTY lets his opponents know that he and his gang are ready to fight them.

Rumble means: Old school NY brawl involving chains, bats, brass knuckles, sometimes knives and other non-lethal weapons to settle rivalries with the street gangs
